      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving power plant delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recent inspection of the rear subframe mounting points and refreshed bushings. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity is robust, with a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing service documented. This is a mechanically sound example of an analog icon, ready for the apex.",
