    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me\u2014super reliable, runs smoothly, and is in really solid shape. Whether you\u2019re headed to work or planning a fun weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to go. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you\u2019re getting a great vehicle that still has so many miles of adventures left in it. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
